name affilauthor
category Package
revision 76924
shortdesc Tag author and affiliation information in a key-value style
longdesc This package provides key-value style author and affiliation
longdesc information tagging in a structured format. Each field has a
longdesc specific name similar to the bib format. We can customize the
longdesc styles as per preferences for article.cls class layout. Instead
longdesc of giving all the information (author and affiliation) in a
longdesc single tag, we can split the information in a format of
longdesc key-value style.
